00:02:05,210 --> 00:02:10,950
=Love of Nirvana=
(Based on Xiao Lou's novel of the same name)

19
00:02:11,190 --> 00:02:14,180
=Episode 30=

20
00:02:16,090 --> 00:02:18,240
I have arranged a place for you.

21
00:02:18,700 --> 00:02:20,190
Just stay here without worry.

22
00:02:21,630 --> 00:02:22,380
Miss Jiang,

23
00:02:22,950 --> 00:02:24,470
you should thank His Majesty quickly.

24
00:02:24,860 --> 00:02:25,950
Your Majesty, I...

25
00:02:25,950 --> 00:02:27,950
I had a close relationship
with your father,

26
00:02:28,630 --> 00:02:30,140
so I will make up all the grievances

27
00:02:30,140 --> 00:02:31,860
you suffered over the years to you.

28
00:02:32,392 --> 00:02:35,032
Are you worried that your master
won't be able to let you go?

29
00:02:35,760 --> 00:02:37,320
I will go and talk to her myself.

30
00:02:38,632 --> 00:02:40,300
Thank you for your kindness,
Your Majesty.

31
00:02:40,856 --> 00:02:42,470
Master is indeed reluctant
to let me go,

32
00:02:43,070 --> 00:02:44,630
even I feel reluctant myself,

33
00:02:45,450 --> 00:02:46,970
but prolonged pain is worse.

34
00:02:47,016 --> 00:02:48,630
Since I have decided
to join the palace

35
00:02:48,696 --> 00:02:50,320
to repay your kindness,
Your Majesty.

36
00:02:50,488 --> 00:02:52,420
I must maintain
a sense of propriety with the past.

37
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:54,420
Your Majesty,

38
00:02:54,440 --> 00:02:56,010
please keep my master outside the palace

39
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:57,576
so I can avoid meeting her every day

40
00:02:58,200 --> 00:02:59,420
and feel embarrassed.

41
00:03:02,510 --> 00:03:03,010
Wei Zhao,

42
00:03:04,380 --> 00:03:07,250
take good care of her master
on my behalf outside the palace.

43
00:03:07,530 --> 00:03:08,510
Do not be negligent.

44
00:03:08,712 --> 00:03:09,510
Yes, Your Majesty.

45
00:03:11,700 --> 00:03:12,530
You must be tired.

46
00:03:13,630 --> 00:03:15,190
Follow Chief Steward Tao and go rest.

47
00:03:17,608 --> 00:03:18,872
Thank you, Your Majesty.

48
00:03:20,104 --> 00:03:21,450
Miss Jiang, this way please.

49
00:03:45,864 --> 00:03:47,272
Do you have something on your mind?

50
00:03:50,510 --> 00:03:51,700
I did not catch Lu Yu.

51
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:53,820
I have let you down, Your Majesty.

52
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:58,200
You rescued Prince Qi's daughter.

53
00:03:58,700 --> 00:04:00,950
This in itself is a great achievement.

54
00:04:01,540 --> 00:04:02,480
My duty as a minister

55
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:04,152
is to share your concerns, Your Majesty.

56
00:04:04,450 --> 00:04:07,080
You and Prince Qi
have a strong brotherhood,

57
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,570
but I thought

58
00:04:08,980 --> 00:04:10,730
this matter was too suspicious.

59
00:04:10,808 --> 00:04:12,480
Prince Qi passed away
many years ago,

60
00:04:12,700 --> 00:04:14,670
so why has a daughter
suddenly appeared now?

61
00:04:15,850 --> 00:04:16,670
I think

62
00:04:17,210 --> 00:04:18,060
regarding this matter,

63
00:04:18,060 --> 00:04:19,710
a thorough investigation is required.

64
00:04:21,030 --> 00:04:22,670
I understand what you mean.

65
00:04:26,150 --> 00:04:26,710
Your Majesty,

66
00:04:27,030 --> 00:04:27,940
Lord Pei seeks to meet.

67
00:04:29,016 --> 00:04:30,530
I pay my respects to you, Your Majesty.

68
00:04:31,530 --> 00:04:32,860
What brings you here?

69
00:04:33,940 --> 00:04:35,790
I heard that Jiang Ci
had entered the palace.

70
00:04:36,440 --> 00:04:38,790
Your Majesty, please allow me
to see her.

71
00:04:42,210 --> 00:04:44,670
There's no need to be so anxious.

72
00:04:45,790 --> 00:04:46,800
Your Majesty, you are kind.

73
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:49,980
Although you recognized
the handwriting of Prince Qi

74
00:04:50,230 --> 00:04:52,240
and determined that the letter
is not forged,

75
00:04:52,392 --> 00:04:53,730
human minds are unpredictable.

76
00:04:54,030 --> 00:04:54,940
Lu Yu is cunning.

77
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:56,360
Perhaps for rebellion,

78
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:58,360
he chose a random girl
just to fool you.

79
00:04:59,300 --> 00:05:00,440
I still think

80
00:05:00,440 --> 00:05:02,530
this matter should be
thoroughly investigated.

81
00:05:02,990 --> 00:05:04,340
Do you mean

82
00:05:04,340 --> 00:05:06,616
we should take him to Guangming Bureau
for investigation?

83
00:05:07,320 --> 00:05:09,440
I am willing to share your burden,
Your Majesty.

84
00:05:10,490 --> 00:05:11,050
Your Majesty,

85
00:05:11,630 --> 00:05:12,990
Prince Qi passed away young,

86
00:05:13,340 --> 00:05:14,610
and you lost your best friend.

87
00:05:14,632 --> 00:05:16,600
Now that you have found
the bloodline of Prince Qi,

88
00:05:16,630 --> 00:05:18,488
there are even handwritten letters
as evidence,

89
00:05:19,050 --> 00:05:19,930
I recommend

90
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:22,750
Prince Qi's daughter be kept
in the palace and treated favorably.

91
00:05:22,820 --> 00:05:23,820
This will demonstrate your

92
00:05:23,900 --> 00:05:25,180
benevolence in promoting family harmony

93
00:05:25,192 --> 00:05:26,344
and fostering goodwill within the clan.

94
00:05:27,050 --> 00:05:28,960
Shaojun only thinks of the best
in everything.

95
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:31,550
But we are not on the same page.

96
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:33,550
Your Majesty,

97
00:05:33,820 --> 00:05:35,080
if we keep people involved

98
00:05:35,096 --> 00:05:36,140
with Lu Yu in the palace,

99
00:05:36,200 --> 00:05:37,512
we will certainly face criticism.

100
00:05:38,870 --> 00:05:40,310
Prince Qi passed away early,

101
00:05:40,930 --> 00:05:43,550
how could I just

102
00:05:43,960 --> 00:05:45,380
leave his orphan alone without a care?

103
00:05:46,690 --> 00:05:48,190
I saw her face,

104
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:51,230
there is resemblance to Prince Qi.

105
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:56,080
She seemed sincere
when she read the letter.

106
00:05:56,344 --> 00:05:57,640
She doesn't seem like an actress.

107
00:05:58,110 --> 00:05:59,320
I believe

108
00:05:59,870 --> 00:06:01,670
she is the daughter of Prince Qi.

109
00:06:03,230 --> 00:06:04,690
I will choose an auspicious day

110
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:07,050
to make her a princess.

111
00:06:11,140 --> 00:06:12,110
Your Majesty is wise.

112
00:06:14,392 --> 00:06:15,550
(Yuchun Pavilion, Palace, Qingkang)

113
00:06:15,550 --> 00:06:16,648
(Minxiu Hall)
Miss Jiang.

114
00:06:16,648 --> 00:06:21,160
(Yuchun Pavilion, Palace, Qingkang)

115
00:06:21,930 --> 00:06:22,690
Miss Jiang,

116
00:06:22,728 --> 00:06:25,384
His Majesty, understanding that you are
newly entered into the palace,

117
00:06:25,460 --> 00:06:27,230
has specially allowed me to select

118
00:06:27,230 --> 00:06:28,712
some clever and obedient ones for you.

119
00:06:28,930 --> 00:06:30,500
If you have any instructions,

120
00:06:30,610 --> 00:06:31,960
you may just call them.

121
00:06:34,030 --> 00:06:35,500
(Minxiu Hall)

122
00:06:35,500 --> 00:06:36,870
Greetings, Miss Jiang.

123
00:06:37,580 --> 00:06:39,370
Greetings, Miss Jiang.

124
00:06:39,550 --> 00:06:40,690
No need to be courteous.

125
00:06:41,380 --> 00:06:42,080
Miss Jiang,

126
00:06:42,248 --> 00:06:45,140
the etiquette between master and servant
in this palace must not be broken.

127
00:06:48,440 --> 00:06:49,490
All of you will be serving

128
00:06:49,630 --> 00:06:51,460
as servants in Yuchun Pavilion
from now on.

129
00:06:51,750 --> 00:06:53,200
Serve Miss Jiang well,

130
00:06:53,370 --> 00:06:54,380
do you understand?

131
00:06:54,930 --> 00:06:55,610
Yes.

132
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:57,050
You may rise.

133
00:07:02,050 --> 00:07:02,960
Miss Jiang,

134
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:04,190
(Liu Cui, Maid, Qingkang)
I'm Liu Cui.

135
00:07:04,380 --> 00:07:06,260
(Liu Cui, Maid, Qingkang)
I will serve you from now on.

136
00:07:22,824 --> 00:07:23,976
Sir, I placed the money here.

137
00:07:24,460 --> 00:07:24,960
Sure.

138
00:07:25,550 --> 00:07:26,140
Take care.

139
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:31,700
Your Lordship!

140
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:32,960
Have a seat.

141
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:33,990
I'll have a bowl of noodles.

142
00:07:33,990 --> 00:07:34,690
No problem.

143
00:07:34,730 --> 00:07:35,340
You may sit.

144
00:07:35,490 --> 00:07:36,190
Wait a moment.

145
00:07:36,210 --> 00:07:36,930
Sure.

146
00:07:50,700 --> 00:07:51,990
Your noodles, Your Lordship.

147
00:07:53,270 --> 00:07:54,040
Sir,

148
00:07:54,810 --> 00:07:57,050
next time I bring someone
to have noodles.

149
00:07:57,368 --> 00:07:59,050
I kindly ask you to cook
with special care

150
00:07:59,140 --> 00:08:01,320
so she can truly enjoy
your culinary skills.

151
00:08:01,340 --> 00:08:02,630
No problem, Your Lordship.

152
00:08:03,730 --> 00:08:04,380
Please enjoy.

153
00:08:04,500 --> 00:08:05,250
Thank you.

154
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:06,080
No problem.

155
00:08:22,990 --> 00:08:23,640
Your Majesty,

156
00:08:24,140 --> 00:08:27,200
reliable servants have been assigned
to Yuchun Pavilion.

157
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:30,750
Instructed them
to serve Miss Jiang well

158
00:08:30,790 --> 00:08:31,700
and not be negligent.

159
00:08:31,760 --> 00:08:32,568
Yes, Your Majesty.

160
00:08:46,770 --> 00:08:47,690
Don't worry.

161
00:08:47,992 --> 00:08:49,384
According to the current situation,

162
00:08:49,430 --> 00:08:51,304
His Majesty is not treating
Miss Jiang foully,

163
00:08:51,690 --> 00:08:53,310
and he even wants
to make her a princess.

164
00:08:54,690 --> 00:08:56,840
His Majesty keeps Jiang Ci in the palace

165
00:08:57,270 --> 00:08:58,340
to show his care,

166
00:08:58,536 --> 00:08:59,864
but he's actually monitoring her.

167
00:09:01,860 --> 00:09:03,690
Rearrange the patrol route

168
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:05,240
and discreetly set up

169
00:09:05,272 --> 00:09:07,016
several patrol points
around Yuchun Pavilion.

170
00:09:07,860 --> 00:09:10,320
His Majesty often mentions Prince Qi,

171
00:09:10,570 --> 00:09:11,980
they seem to share a deep connection.

172
00:09:12,510 --> 00:09:14,200
Would he put Prince Qi under
house arrest

173
00:09:14,296 --> 00:09:15,390
as what the Yans said?

174
00:09:16,150 --> 00:09:18,070
If what the Yans said is true,

175
00:09:18,340 --> 00:09:20,340
the reason His Majesty
interrupted Prince Qi's case

176
00:09:21,050 --> 00:09:23,150
must have some unspoken truth behind it.

177
00:09:24,150 --> 00:09:26,810
We need to be more cautious
in our investigation.

178
00:09:29,496 --> 00:09:30,600
Send a message to Mr. Ping

179
00:09:30,930 --> 00:09:33,220
to get Shadow Sect to put in
even more attention

180
00:09:33,272 --> 00:09:34,264
and to always be prepared.

181
00:09:34,730 --> 00:09:35,560
Yes.

182
00:09:35,770 --> 00:09:39,070
(Lord of Jianding's Residence)

183
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:40,008
Lord of Jianding

184
00:09:40,056 --> 00:09:41,110
has stabilized internal chaos

185
00:09:41,110 --> 00:09:42,220
and promoted military reforms.

186
00:09:42,220 --> 00:09:44,860
Madam Rongguo must have
taught him very well.

187
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:47,930
I am just a mere woman.

188
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:50,620
What I care most about is
the blessings of my family.

189
00:09:52,810 --> 00:09:54,440
Lord Hou is in his prime

190
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:56,376
and he made another
great achievement this time.

191
00:09:56,580 --> 00:09:58,960
Why worry about
a good match for him?

192
00:09:59,570 --> 00:10:00,720
A beautiful marriage

193
00:10:00,744 --> 00:10:02,648
emphasizes the importance of
matching social status.

194
00:10:08,810 --> 00:10:11,690
These are his birth date
and ancestral place of origin.

195
00:10:12,430 --> 00:10:15,220
Chancellor Dong, please discuss this
with Second Young Lady.

196
00:10:19,592 --> 00:10:22,030
I have troubled you for quite a while
at your residence today.

197
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:24,270
I should make my move.

198
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:26,340
Thank you for taking the time for this.

199
00:10:26,728 --> 00:10:27,864
-Goodbye.
-This way, please.

200
00:10:28,100 --> 00:10:28,890
Here.

201
00:10:31,050 --> 00:10:31,720
Chancellor Dong.

202
00:10:43,928 --> 00:10:45,510
A distinguished guest came to our house,

203
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:48,150
why didn't you say a word?

204
00:10:49,810 --> 00:10:51,100
You are occupied with work,

205
00:10:51,460 --> 00:10:54,080
how can I tell you everything in detail?

206
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:56,120
Including marriage?

207
00:11:00,888 --> 00:11:03,288
Second Young Lady Dong is chaste,
virtuous, and gentle.

208
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:04,440
She will be a good match.

209
00:11:05,580 --> 00:11:07,960
If one day in the future,
you truly become a virtuous ruler

210
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:10,340
you can win back the hearts
of the top clans.

211
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:13,840
This is never what I want.

212
00:11:25,100 --> 00:11:26,700
This marriage

213
00:11:27,270 --> 00:11:28,810
will only benefit you.

214
00:11:29,220 --> 00:11:30,460
Can't you understand?

215
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:34,320
If I can give you what you want

216
00:11:34,820 --> 00:11:36,390
in another way?

217
00:11:37,340 --> 00:11:38,360
Jiang Ci

218
00:11:39,340 --> 00:11:40,860
is the daughter of Prince Qi.

219
00:11:44,100 --> 00:11:45,270
Daughter of Prince Qi?

220
00:11:45,560 --> 00:11:48,216
His Majesty attaches great importance
to the bloodline of Prince Qi.

221
00:11:48,232 --> 00:11:49,944
Jiang Ci has not returned
to the capital yet,

222
00:11:49,992 --> 00:11:51,688
but she is given
a residence in the palace.

223
00:11:51,930 --> 00:11:52,700
She will soon

224
00:11:53,190 --> 00:11:54,930
become a princess.

225
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:01,050
Since you have the request,

226
00:12:01,736 --> 00:12:04,510
you will naturally understand
which of Dong family or the royal family

227
00:12:05,860 --> 00:12:07,240
would be more helpful.

228
00:12:09,340 --> 00:12:10,810
Jiang Ci

229
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:15,320
is what I want in my life.

230
00:12:29,860 --> 00:12:32,530
Lord Pei seems determined
to marry Jiang Ci.

231
00:12:34,010 --> 00:12:34,810
Madam,

232
00:12:35,050 --> 00:12:36,570
are you going to let him?

233
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:41,120
Yan still doesn't quite understand
His Majesty.

234
00:12:41,810 --> 00:12:43,100
I didn't expect

235
00:12:43,430 --> 00:12:45,670
that Jiang Ci is
the daughter of Prince Qi.

236
00:12:52,930 --> 00:12:54,890
Mr. Cui, it is difficult
to get you to paint.

237
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:56,740
I am really blessed to have this.

238
00:12:56,760 --> 00:12:59,030
I will certainly help to find
a good buyer for this painting.

239
00:12:59,700 --> 00:13:01,320
I paint as I please.

240
00:13:01,510 --> 00:13:02,650
You can

241
00:13:02,824 --> 00:13:04,220
sell paintings as you please, too.

242
00:13:16,220 --> 00:13:17,270
Sir, please wait.

243
00:13:18,690 --> 00:13:20,170
Can you show me the painting?

244
00:13:21,700 --> 00:13:22,510
Thank you.

245
00:13:28,190 --> 00:13:28,740
Jin Xin.

246
00:13:33,590 --> 00:13:34,290
Here.

247
00:13:35,080 --> 00:13:36,930
Miss, are you buying it just like that?

248
00:13:37,432 --> 00:13:38,570
I buy paintings as I please.

249
00:13:38,650 --> 00:13:39,740
Please do not judge me.

250
00:13:40,410 --> 00:13:41,030
Thank you.

251
00:13:47,650 --> 00:13:49,080
Come and take a look.

252
00:13:49,270 --> 00:13:50,770
Sachets for sale.

253
00:13:51,690 --> 00:13:52,840
Come and take a look.

254
00:13:52,848 --> 00:13:54,510
(Jixian Study)

255
00:14:36,030 --> 00:14:37,080
Excuse me,

256
00:14:37,720 --> 00:14:38,890
I have embarrassed myself.

257
00:14:42,600 --> 00:14:43,410
Mr. Cui?

258
00:14:44,170 --> 00:14:44,860
Mr. Cui,

259
00:14:44,888 --> 00:14:46,150
it's good that you are still here.

260
00:14:46,150 --> 00:14:46,740
Your painting

261
00:14:46,930 --> 00:14:49,170
has been purchased by a lady
for a good price.

262
00:14:50,930 --> 00:14:52,220
The lady is here.

263
00:14:54,650 --> 00:14:56,190
All these are yours.

264
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:00,430
I shall take my leave.

265
00:15:05,460 --> 00:15:08,030
It turns out that the paintings
were all yours.

266
00:15:08,690 --> 00:15:11,120
Have you bought my paintings before?

267
00:15:12,070 --> 00:15:13,080
Yes.

268
00:15:14,930 --> 00:15:15,700
I am ashamed.

269
00:15:16,410 --> 00:15:17,960
It is an honor for me

270
00:15:18,200 --> 00:15:19,720
to receive your favor.

271
00:15:20,430 --> 00:15:21,220
You may take

272
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:23,120
this painting as a gift from me.

273
00:15:26,570 --> 00:15:28,190
Gold cannot buy
what one truly cherishes.

274
00:15:29,030 --> 00:15:30,940
Your painting is worth the price.

