Are you not afraid
that your unborn child

352
00:20:23,420 --> 00:20:24,400
will get punished?

353
00:20:24,420 --> 00:20:25,230
Shut your mouth!

354
00:20:26,340 --> 00:20:27,160
There is an assassin!

355
00:20:32,600 --> 00:20:33,400
